OL,3,CVladimir Putin would have ordered
OL,4,CSalisbury Novichok poisoning, inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"It is His Majesty's Government's view
OL,8,Fthat President Putin authorised the
OL,9,Foperation".
OL,11,FThose were the words of Jonathan
OL,12,FAllen, a senior Foreign Office
OL,13,Fofficial, on the attempted
OL,14,Fassassination of former Russian agent
OL,15,FSergei Skripal and his daughter Yulia
OL,16,Fin Salisbury in 2018.
