OL,3,CVladimir Putin would have ordered
OL,4,CSalisbury Novichok poisoning, inquiry
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Allen said the UK had learned from
OL,8,Fthe death of Alexander Litvinenko,
OL,9,Fanother former Russian agent who was
OL,10,Ffatally poisoned with polonium in
OL,11,FLondon in 2006.
OL,13,F"Russia played all sorts of games,
OL,14,Fplayed with the police investigation
OL,15,Fand ultimately the inquiry, pretending
OL,16,Fthat it was going to cooperate and
OL,17,Fnever doing so.
