OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FSo there was absolute clarity from the
OL,8,Fstart that we were not going to let
OL,9,FRussia string this out in the same
OL,10,Fway," he said.
OL,12,FHe said Russia would have been "quite
OL,13,Fshocked" at the speed of the
OL,14,Finternational response to the
OL,15,Fpoisoning of the Skripals, which
OL,16,Fincluded the expulsion of 153 Russian
OL,17,Fintelligence operatives from 29
OL,18,Fcountries.
